thread.title: Anat Gamerov
thread.title_full: Fesal recensione scritta da Anat Gamerov

author: Anat Gamerov
title: Anat Gamerov
text:
Hi , my name is Anat , and I am from
Australia. Yes , it is a very far away place to start and import to but thanks to the most amazing service and understanding I have imported a container , full of amazing goods from my electrical to taps and sinks . All top quality and much cheaper . If you are building a new Home I highly recommend to use Fessal
You can save a lot . They make it really easy to import , everything is organized for you.
I have to thank Fillipo for his unbelievable service, 10 out of 10.
Thank you .
